# Project's website

Website published at https://mesasdecultivo.surge.sh

Website based on [hexo](https://hexo.io/), a fast, simple and powerful blog framework.
Internal theme layout based on [PugJS](https://pugjs.org/api/getting-started.html).

## Installation

- Install docker, docker-compose, make
- Clone this repo
- Run make install to install all the dependences
- Run make start to build the project
- Visit the website at http://localhost:4000

